VERSION	3.0
actions
  global code
    For code outside any function
      Parameters :
        global code		indicator	.*
      some languages, such as perl, sh or vim allow
      code outside any function.
      This is handled here.
      Example :	truer -noIntro -noSharpBang -noProtos
	global code
	  "running"
    >
	${cc}Code outside any function
      $offset-=2;
    <
      $offset+=2;
